title: Race & Win: Making the Best of Your Crew
description: Serving as the ultimate audiovisual reference for racing crews and America's Cup hopefuls, this educational program hosted by racing coach Tucker Thompson offers a detailed look at the mechanics involved in each individual crew position on a modern race boat. Professional sailors lead you through segments that focus on the responsibilities of the bow, mast, pit, headsail trimmer, main trimmer, tailer, tacks, jibes and douses.
